# Placeholder so `visual-baselines/` exists in the repo even when no
# baseline PNGs are committed yet. The PNGs themselves are gitignored
# locally (see .gitignore) and arrive via the
# update-visual-baselines.yml workflow which force-stages them. Once
# that workflow's PR merges, real baseline PNGs live alongside this
# file — keep it untouched so the directory is never accidentally
# removed during a `rm -rf visual-baselines/*` (it skips dotfiles).
